FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our delicious dog treats
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What ingredients do you use in your dog treats?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: We use only high-quality, natural ingredients sourced from trusted suppliers. Our treats are made with real meat, fruits, and vegetables, with no artificial preservatives or additives.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Are your treats suitable for dogs with allergies?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We offer a range of hypoallergenic treats suitable for dogs with common food sensitivities. Always check the ingredient list and consult with your veterinarian if you have concerns about your dog's specific allergies.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How long do your treats last?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Our treats have a shelf life of 12 months when stored in a cool, dry place. Once opened, we recommend using them within 4-6 weeks for optimal freshness.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Do you offer treats for puppies?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, we have a special line of puppy-friendly treats that are softer and sized appropriately for younger dogs. These treats are also formulated to support healthy growth and development.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How often can I give my dog your treats?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: While our treats are healthy and nutritious, they should be given in moderation as part of a balanced diet. We recommend following the feeding guidelines on the package and adjusting based on your dog's size, age, and activity level.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Pawsome Treats
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What makes your dog treats special?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our treats are made with all-natural, high-quality ingredients, specially formulated to support your dog's health and happiness. We use no artificial preservatives, colors, or flavors, ensuring your furry friend gets only the best.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Are your treats suitable for dogs with allergies?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes! We offer a range of hypoallergenic treats made with novel proteins and limited ingredients. Always check the ingredient list and consult with your vet if your dog has specific dietary requirements.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How often can I give these treats to my dog?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: While our treats are healthy and nutritious, they should be given in moderation as part of a balanced diet. The exact amount depends on your dog's size, age, and activity level. We recommend following the feeding guidelines on the package or consulting with your veterinarian.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Do you offer a satisfaction guarantee?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! We stand behind the quality of our treats. If you or your furry friend are not completely satisfied with your purchase, we offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. Just contact our customer service team, and we'll make it right.
